name: Fuji Kawaguchiko Dusk
description:
(to-ma-re series) 

Kawaguchiko is a lake located at the feet of Mount Fuji. In the blue dusk, this giant mountain is as elusive as ever—ghostly, hovering over the town and its streets.

‘To-ma-re’ is the Japanese reading of the ‘stop’ sign featured in every illustration in the series.
